::Kaiser/The Dragoon::
       The Dragoon simply turns and walks to the door and transforms into his 
drake beast mode.  He takes off into the air and circles the base.

       Kaiser shrugs.  "I've said my piece, let us depart."  He too walks 
outside and transforms into his griffin mode.  He paws lightly at the ground 
eager to leave.
